    <section title="Self Assessments">
        
        <page type="quiz" title="Question 1">
            
            <multipleChoiceSingle retry="true">
                
                <question image="" audio="">
                    <![CDATA[<p><strong>I'm not sure I was clear, should you burn the butter or not?</strong></p>]]>
                </question>
                <choices>
                    
                    <answer image="" audio="">
                        <value>Yes</value>
                        <feedback><![CDATA[Sorry, I <strong>misspoke</strong>. Don't burn the butter.]]></feedback>
                    </answer>
                    
                    <answer image="" audio="" correct="yes">
                        <value>No</value>
                        <feedback><![CDATA[That's right, we don't want <strong>burnt</strong> butter in our cookies.]]></feedback>
                    </answer>
                    
                    <answer image="" audio="">
                        <value>It depends on personal taste</value>
                        <feedback><![CDATA[Personally, I don't think you should burn the butter. But if you indeed like burnt butter in your cookies, go ahead.]]></feedback>
                    </answer>
                    
                </choices>
                
            </multipleChoiceSingle>
            
        </page>
        
        <page type="quiz" title="Question 2">
            
            <shortAnswer>
                
                <question image="" audio=""><![CDATA[What are your main take aways from this presentation?]]></question>
                <feedback>I was hoping you would be surprised to hear how relatively young the Chocolate Chip cookie is. I am also hoping you noticed how important getting the ingredients right is to having good results.</feedback>
                
            </shortAnswer>
            
        </page>
        
